Package: cewl
Version: 6.2.1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, ruby, pkg-config, openssl, libxml2, libxslt, ruby-nokogiri, exiftool
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/digininja/CeWL
Description: Custom Word List generator (CeWL) for password cracking
 CeWL (Custom Word List generator) is a Ruby tool that spiders a target website
 to create a wordlist for password cracking tools like John the Ripper or Hashcat.
 It supports depth crawling, metadata extraction, and more.
